name: You Punks Get Off My Lawn

metadata.name: You Punks Get Off My Lawn 01
metadata.description: When they're not flipping jpegs, these crypto boomers are busy tending their lawns and yelling at the digital sky. A tongue in cheek project honoring both the og nft collection, and what's left of my graying hair. Owners will have early access to future airdrops, collections and irl merchandise by Ills Supply Co.
